  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/87654375/PTI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PTI</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jun 9, 2026 at 07:29 AM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>Mumbai: <a href=\"/tag/p.+d.+hinduja+hospital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">P. D. Hinduja Hospital</a> &amp; Medical Research Centre on Monday signed an agreement with Dr <a href=\"/tag/homi+bhabha+state+university\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Homi Bhabha State University</a> (HBSU) to jointly conduct postgraduate allied (paramedical) health courses.The hospital has been offering allied health sciences <a href=\"/tag/skill-based+education\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">skill-based education</a> in strategic partnership with the Lifesupporters Institute of Health Sciences (LIHS) for over a decade, P. D. Hinduja Hospital &amp; Medical Research Centre said in a statement.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>This memorandum of understanding (MoU) aims to address the growing demand for skilled healthcare professionals and strengthen the quality of paramedical education in India.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>The program, expected to commence in August, will be offered across multiple specialised areas with an intake of 20-30 students per course.Skill-based postgraduate certificate programs will be offered as Pathology Technician, Dialysis Technician, Operation Theatre Technician (OT), Intensive Care Unit Technician (ICU), Radiology Technician, Medical Records &amp; Health Information Technician, Neurology Technician, Central Sterile Supply Department Technician (CSSD), and Endoscopy Technician.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>\"As healthcare increasingly becomes specialised, there is a pressing need to build a strong workforce equipped with practical knowledge and clinical expertise. Through this collaboration with Dr Homi Bhabha State University, we aim to train industry-ready, highly skilled allied healthcare professionals capable of delivering quality and safe patient care,\" P. D. Hinduja Hospital &amp; Medical Research Centre CEO Gautam Khanna added.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                    \n\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/87654375/PTI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PTI</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jun 9, 2026 at 07:29 AM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jun 9, 2026 at 07:29 AM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-app-store.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                        </div>    -->\n                         \n                \n                                    <figure>\n                        <!-- <i></i>\n                        <span class=\"scan-text\">Scan to download App</span> -->\n                        <img src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/bar-codes/health_barcode.png?mod=3344\" alt=\"\">                        \n                        <!-- <span class=\"border-bottom\"></span> -->\n                    </figure>\n                            \n       \n\n\n                    \n                \n            "
